♫  It's pointless to look for excuses  ♫

245
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:07,368
♫  Stop backing down  ♫

246
00:22:09,672 --> 00:22:12,768
♫  I want you to know that time waits for no one  ♫

247
00:22:12,768 --> 00:22:17,680
♫  We must never give up  ♫

248
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:23,812
♫  Let's break, destroy, and burn empty promises  ♫

249
00:22:23,812 --> 00:22:28,460
♫  Fearlessly, we keep marching forward  ♫

250
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:31,528
♫  I'm going against the tide  ♫

251
